description: F9Fast is back June 25.http://www.thefastsaga.com/No matter how fast you are, no one outruns their past. F9 is the ninth chapter in the Fast & Furious Saga, which has endured for two decades and has earned more than $5 billion around the world.  Vin Dieselâ€™s Dom Toretto is leading a quiet life off the grid with Letty and his son, little Brian, but they know that danger always lurks just over their peaceful horizon. This time, that threat will force Dom to confront the sins of his past if heâ€™s going to save those he loves most. His crew joins together to stop a world-shattering plot led by the most skilled assassin and high-performance driver theyâ€™ve ever encountered: a man who also happens to be Domâ€™s forsaken brother, Jakob (John Cena, the upcoming The Suicide Squad). F9 sees the return of Justin Lin as director, who helmed the third, fourth, fifth and sixth chapters of the series when it transformed into a global blockbuster. The action hurtles around the globeâ€”from London to Tokyo, from Central America to Edinburgh, and from a secret bunker in Azerbaijan to the teeming streets of Tbilisi. Along the way, old friends will be resurrected, old foes will return, history will be rewritten, and the true meaning of family will be tested like never before.  The film stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris â€œLudacrisâ€ Bridges, Jordana Brewster, Nathalie Emmanuel and Sung Kang, with OscarÂ® winner Helen Mirren and OscarÂ® winner Charlize Theron. F9 also features Grammy-winning superstar Cardi B as new franchise character Leysa, a woman with a connection to Domâ€™s past, and a cameo by Reggaeton sensation Ozuna.  F9 is produced by Neal H. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. First of all, best wishes for Navratri 2020 to all of you. During the 9 days of holy festival of Navratri, nine forms of Goddess Durga are worshiped and each day is dedicated to an incarnation of Goddess Mother. As we all know, there are different forms of Goddess. Today is the first of the auspicious nine days of Navratri which is dedicated to Goddess Shailaputri.Shailaputri, daughter of the mountains, is a avatar of the goddess, Durga. She is one of the first Navadurga venerated during the first day of Navratri. She is also known as Sati, Bhavani, Parvati or Hemavati.Shailaputri mata ( #shailputrimata ) is the absolute form of Mother Nature. Mata Shailputri is born from a rock or a mountain, so worshiping her brings stability in life. With proper worship of Mata Shailputri, marital life remains happy and happiness comes to your family. Their archana awakens the muladhara chakra, which results in the development of vitality and enthusiasm in life. At the same time, on the first day of Navratri, by worshiping mother Shailaputri, all kinds of defects associated with the moon are removed and good fortune is achieved.  We should listen #navratrikatha of maa Shailputri  on day 1 of navratri for her blessings. Maa Shailputri ki katha shows who is devi shailputri. How devi got this name of Shailputri ? This video also shows Shailputri Aarti, shailputri mantra , shailputri kavach, and shailputri stotram.

description: Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:--------------------------------------------------------------------The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu.
